properties.headline: COVID-19 Pop-up drive-through clinic - ROSELANDS Roselands Shopping Centre in car park
properties.otherAdvice:
A 24/7 COVID-19 pop-up drive-through clinic is now operating at the Roselands Shopping Centre open-air car park.

No booking is required.

Delays may be experienced for those queuing for testing.

Visit the NSW Health website for a full list of other testing locations.

properties.headline: HAZARD Landslip - TUENA (SOUTH OF BLAYNEY) Abercrombie Road near Abercrombie River (60km north of Crookwell)
properties.otherAdvice:
Portable traffic signals are in place to allow motorists to pass in one direction at a time.

Motorists are advised to allow approximately 10 minutes of additional travel time.

A width restriction of 3.1m is in place. Vehicles wider than 3.1m need to use an alternative route.

From Monday 8 November, work will be carried out for approximately three weeks from 7am to 6pm on weekdays and 8am to 1pm on Saturdays. The road will be closed for one hour periods and will open on the hour for five minute intervals during work hours. Motorists are advised to plan their journey around the opening times.
